##############################################################################
## (Description)
##    Imake file for tt_thresh_new.
##	clean    : to clean the directory.
##	cleanall : to remove everything reproducible.
## (Update Record) 
##    94/11/25  K.Fujii 	Original.
##    97/08/30  K.Fujii 	Use 97a.
##
